name: Wrong Computed Total Amount
description:
The amount computed doesn't match with the external amount.
Please fix it manually.
NB : This check have being applyed because you check the option 'check total amount' on the shop of this sale order
code:
if order.shop_id.check_total_amount and abs(order.amount_total - order.ext_total_amount) >= 0.01:
    failed = True
